# Manual requests for each scenario (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP).
# Endpoints are implemented across M1–M7; this file grows with them.

@gateway = http://localhost:8080

### Login (M1) -> returns USER JWT
POST {{gateway}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "maria", "password": "demo123" }

